{"tid":2236091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[回力鏢系列] 陳帆稱公共交通費用補貼門檻定於400元屬合理水平","createTime":"2020-10-09T08:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T12:31:07.000Z","uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68524a8b77d46c592a2760b8a797936d261770df","tid":2236091,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，公共交通費用補貼計劃的政策目的，在於支援公共交通開支較高的市民，受較多資助的市民一般居於較偏遠地方，認為目前將每月補貼門檻定於400元，屬合理水平。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆又說，計劃實行之後，政府平均每月提供約1.6億元補貼，220萬人受惠，人均補貼為73元，每月平均159萬人領取100元以下津貼、44萬人領取101元至200元津貼、大約12萬人可領取約200元至300元津貼。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯議員陳恒鑌認為，人均獲津貼73元，反映補貼門檻高，即使補貼率及補貼上限提升，受惠人數依然不多。陳帆回應說，政府要以審慎理財為前提，確保公帑運用得宜，又指如果將交通費補貼門檻下調至每月200元，補貼金額會由31億增加至58億元，而計劃運作情況將於今年第四季檢討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502903-20200115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502903-20200115.htm&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=1a3a9d01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502903-20200115.htm&h=eb83677d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502903-20200115.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3607cce8b9988e3ae5461365b75e7b4ad452ecad","tid":2236091,"uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"陳帆回應說，政府要以審慎理財為前提，確保公帑運用得宜，又指如果將交通費補貼門檻下調至每月200元，補貼金額會由31億增加至58億元<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2020-01-15 HKT 13:23</span><br />\n<br />\n唔使一年，回力鏢又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992d4a820ba39ecf304c8469687ecd37a719c512","tid":2236091,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"公共交通費用補貼計劃開支水平下月至年底放寬至二百元<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-29 HKT 17:51<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534721-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534721-20200629.htm&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=d8bca958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534721-20200629.htm&h=ddd5a76a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534721-20200629.htm</a>"},{"pid":"03ac9c9226f8250cd679615d3e942694f8392d8e","tid":2236091,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce3663ddb9f42e10c1903c779067745b748cf272","tid":2236091,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"合理 從來都唔使拎"}]}